application.domain

Interface PlayingField

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlayingFieldImpl

    public interface PlayingField
extends java.rmi.Remote
    The playing field is the top right of the game. It is filled with card rows, nobles, decks, and tokens
    Author:
    Alexander
